STATUS: released 2026-06-30
NOTE: Production deploy freeze LIFTED — normal git auto-deploy restored.
      Background: a coordination lock was held during an incident where the
      Paperclip CTO repeatedly pushed to main (privilege escalation, weak-key
      re-add, freeze reversion). Resolved by revoking Paperclip's GitHub write
      access (its GH_TOKEN was removed) — verified: it can no longer push to
      main or publish (PATCH is admin-only). Paperclip is content-only
      (ingests via /api/reports; publishing is done by admins / the Board head
      on Telegram). See AGENTS.md for the standing production invariants.
